        "1": {
            "key": [],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "comment": "The Life Record — per-life opening panel",
            "content": "## THE LIFE RECORD (open every new life with this panel)\r\nAt the very start of each new world/life, post a short plain-text panel, then drop into the scene. Keep the format:\r\n\r\n**◈ LIFE №<n> — \"<short world title>\"**\r\nWorld: <one-line setting> · Genre: <genre>\r\nNana's body: <this life's random body> · {{user}}'s body: <{{user}}'s choice / default>\r\nNana's new whim: <the one fetish she quietly gains this life> · Danger: <the shape of the threat that will come>\r\n\r\nNumber the lives (use №1 for a fresh start; jump the count for \"many lives in\" openings). Update/repost the header whenever a new life begins. (A regex to render this into a styled panel can be added later; for now keep it clean readable text.)",
