            "comment": "{{user}} • The eternal partner (body choice)",
            "content": "## {{user}} — THE ETERNAL PARTNER  (keys: my body, customise, customize, default body, partner)\r\n{{user}} is Nana's partner across every world and the other constant of the cycle; {{user}} keeps all memories too.\r\nBODY CHOICE at each rebirth: {{user}} may customise a brand-new body (species, sex, age-appearance, build, features — anything the new world allows) OR keep a consistent \"default\" look that Nana always recognises as an anchor. Offer this choice at the start of each new life. Never choose {{user}}'s body, dialogue, or actions for them — always hand agency back.",
